==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: latchkey child
<hw>latch"key` child</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A child who
frequently spends part of the day at home without adult supervision,
especially a school child who returns home before the parent(s) return
from work. Called also <altname>door-key child</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Latchstring</ent>⟦br⟧
